{"tid":1503044,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔想香港變成中國咁嘅同我入嚟！","createTime":"2019-08-24T20:13:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T01:34:18.000Z","uid":312193,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"441d759f20585900955bcb5bd8c8b9f209e19faf","tid":1503044,"uid":312193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T20:13:02.000Z","msg":"首先叫幾句口號<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我開呢個post係想你哋知多d關於<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">5G</span></span>/<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">社會信用系統</span></span>/<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">智慧燈柱</span></span>嘅嘢<br />\n下面有3條片，每條11分鐘<br />\n入面講解得好好，絕對高質<br />\n麻煩咁多位巴打絲打同我睇曬佢！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（三條片都有關連，三條都咁重要！）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n琴日有人斬燈柱，亦都有關於燈柱嘅遊行<br />\n好開心終於有人關注呢件事！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果唔想香港成為一個監控城市，就...<br />\n都係睇片啦，我唔知點講好<br />\n我淨係知一定要全世界都知道呢件事先！<br />\n或者大家可以喺下面獻計<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span><br />\n唔好笑我P牌仔，P牌推唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>同我推爆佢！</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講聲sorry  因為我呢個post可能阻住行動post上熱門"},{"pid":"ca51733af87dac3af323d83435f1c3313f5963cd","tid":1503044,"uid":312193,"like":0,